\cf4 \cb5 A research analyst is attempting to calculate the unlevered beta for an industry. The levered beta for a company with a debt-to-equity ratio of 30% and a tax rate of 20% is 1.3. What is the unlevered beta for this company?\cb1 \
\cb5 QID:\'a02840156\cb1 \
\cb5 Mark For Review\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0\fs60 \cf4 \cb6 A\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\fs34 \cf4 \cb6 1.0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs60 \cf8 \'a0\'a0\'a0\cb1 \
