\cf4 \cb5 An Italian manufacturer of high-end eyewear has announced it will acquire a U.S. producer of a popular brand of sunglasses. When the deal closes, the U.S. dollar has weakened against the euro. What is the impact of the currency fluctuation?\cb1 \
\cb5 QID:\'a02840258\cb1 \
