\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\fs34 \cf4 \cb6 The Italian company is likely to purchase other U.S. companies as well\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\fs60 \cf4 C\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\fs34 \cf4 \cb6 It would increase the cost of the acquisition\
