\f0\b\fs34 \cf4 \cb5 Lotus Engineering entered the electronic damper control industry 10 years ago with an innovative design. The company introduced new products in its 4th and 6th years in the industry. Based on the exhibit above showing revenues and sales, what would you conclude about Lotus Engineering and the industry?\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb5 QID:\'a02840208\cb1 \
\cb5 Mark For Review\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs60 \cf11 \cb6 \'a0\'a0\'a0\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs34 \cf9 \cb6 Lotus is a growth company in a growth industry\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0\fs60 \cf4 B\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\fs34 \cf4 \cb6 Lotus' revenues have increased at a faster rate than the industry\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs60 \cf8 \'a0\'a0\'a0\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0\fs34 \cf4 \cb6 Competition has entered the market and eroded Lotus' ability to charge a premium price\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\fs60 \cf4 D\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl600\partightenfactor0

\fs34 \cf4 \cb6 Lotus has increased market share through predatory pricing\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs47\fsmilli23800 \cf12 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl1180\partightenfactor0
\cf9 \cb5 INCORRECT ANSWER CHOSEN\cf12 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f7\i\b0\fs34 \cf4 \cb5 The industry showed more rapid growth than Lotus over the 10-year period. Industry revenue growth was 125% ([$142 MM - $63 MM] / $63 MM). Lotus revenue growth was 107%. Lotus had much higher unit sales growth than the industry. It was 200% for Lotus ([35,100 - 11,700] / 11,700), while the industry unit sales growth was 154% ([177,500 - 70,000] / 70,000). Competition eroded the company's competitive advantage and forced down the prices. In the case of Lotus, unit prices declined by 31% while, in the industry, prices declined by 11%.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa272\partightenfactor0

